pan>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\">8.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-1\">8.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_12\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 12\">Chapter 12</a>, Cersei III.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\">9.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-1\">9.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_16\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 16\">Chapter 16</a>, Jaime II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_36\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 36\">Chapter 36</a>, Cersei VIII.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403193950\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.106 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.296 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1795/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 11352/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 16188/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 2352/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 12/40\nExpensive pars